QuestData.Title: WANTED: Keeho's Severed Paw
QuestData.Description: Posted by: Taskmaster Gornek$B$BThe saberon known as Keeho poses a serious threat to Axefall.$B$BHe has taken to slaughtering peons on the night shift and dragging their corpses to his den in the pridelands.$B$BAnyone who can bring me his severed paw as proof of his demise will be rewarded greatly.
QuestData.LogDescription: Retrieve Keeho's Severed Paw from Keeho the Savage.
QuestData.RewardText: The peons will sing songs of your glory, commander. Lok'tar ogar!
